{"tid":2021783,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"西營盤 “泰道” 泰國菜館","createTime":"2020-05-18T02:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T07:46:25.000Z","uid":253069,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc13389ff810fcdf5da4437145ce70a9c2a2894d","tid":2021783,"uid":253069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"依間係我一位朋友泰國媽咪開既餐廳，食物質素係高同分量偏多既.價錢我會話公道.缺點我會話店面有細少少, 有機會坐得唔舒服.不過無計鋪面有D細<br />\n<br />\n主打菜式<br />\n1.) 泰式炆原隻豬手 ($128) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQgHCYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQgHCYt.jpg&h=d8ea40a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食落去啖啖肉，口感滿分<br />\n<br />\n2.) 傳統風味鮮蝦冬蔭公 細($88)/ 大($ 148)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zbSGTxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzbSGTxj.jpg&h=0d70cd0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯頭用新鮮原隻大蝦去熬, 配埋南薑, 香茅，紅辣椒調味.完全係合格之上既傳統冬蔭公.<br />\n<br />\n3.) 媽媽乾咖哩 ($ 85) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLmkpEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLmkpEu.png&h=71386602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n濃郁椰香加埋花生味道, 我會話係送飯之選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4sWHrr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4sWHrr.jpg&h=76087c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有問過果位泰國媽咪點解開餐廳，佢話開餐廳係一直以黎既夢想, 其次係希望將地道泰菜帶過黎香港.<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以click 入去睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bangkokexpresshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbangkokexpresshk&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=f2fcb44b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bangkokexpresshk</a><br />\n<br />\n地點:西營盤西邊街2號D地下鋪（港鐵西營盤站B3出口步行3分鐘）"},{"pid":"5630c34c86d735eafeb3d48e29b46eae57299c42","tid":2021783,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:59:56.000Z","msg":"似好食"},{"pid":"38f174381172503cb909d9bf1063a82959c0fdc6","tid":2021783,"uid":263691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65b36ab4de531255ef1ba7d7b70f67356241140","tid":2021783,"uid":253069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38f174381172503cb909d9bf1063a82959c0fdc6","tid":2021783,"uid":263691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"清一色黃既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0925ce434d63f08a51f4d4c611986ab9a32434","tid":2021783,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5429659606e61126df1dda326f56bf3246168a2c","tid":2021783,"uid":28193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"SOR, 黃都好, 接受唔到你係度賣廣告。"},{"pid":"88de444d36c1e1d2d30b330da2223bd54ab1be10","tid":2021783,"uid":165184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"係幾好<br />\n好過狗屋隔離果間<br />\n萍姐好似藍<br />\n<br />\n但感覺比之前再上一手遜色<br />\n（果個位第一間泰國鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 之後好似有人頂咗手差咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 再到泰道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n利申：成日食肉碎蛋飯，隻蛋好好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5f94e509bd5249a97390af559ef60e9e24e10f","tid":2021783,"uid":46151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"38f174381172503cb909d9bf1063a82959c0fdc6","tid":2021783,"uid":263691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"上得嚟賣廣告嘅 點都話自己黃㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb88a51d9043a9c8c64c85a31c30513008ca9de6","tid":2021783,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1dadde71488e2fd0426e67d6f389d7b2b6869d","tid":2021783,"uid":91741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"食開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老細時唔時都會屌尻政府弱智"}]}